EN: The two countries have been debating on how to combat terrorism.
ZH: 8. 我们必须对抗人们的偏见和歧视。
EN: We must fight against people's prejudices and discrimination.
ZH: 9. 这场战斗是为了对抗不公正的制度。
EN: This battle is to resist against an unjust system.
ZH: 10. 他毅然决定面对并对抗自己的内心恶魔。
EN: He courageously decided to confront and battle his inner demons.
