EN: These soldiers have undergone rigorous training to face war.
ZH: 18. 我们应该团结起来，对抗任何形式的不平等。
EN: We should unite and resist any form of inequality.
ZH: 19. 通过教育，我们可以对抗无知和偏见。
EN: Through education, we can combat ignorance and prejudice.
